    \end {tikzcd}


 To show the adjunction, let c\xrightarrow {m} x and d\xrightarrow {n} y be maps. Then
  f^*n is the pullback of n along f, so that a map m\xrightarrow {g} f^*n in
  C/x is a commutative diagram 




